Rion:

Rion yelled back over his shoulder:

"Run FASTER!!!"

Rion nearly jumped when moments later Diana appeared at his side. She was 
definitely fast. And she wanted him to --what?!--

"Nuh uh!"

Rion realized that by land he was at a disadvantage. His wings snapped 
outward, spreading to their full condorian length. With several beats he 
became airborne. Two more and he nearly doubled his speed. He made a beeline 
for the trees. Trees equaled safety. They'd be safe there, they had to be...
